#. <CLT 04>図書館に着いた。<CLT>
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Here we are at the school store...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>大きな建物の中には見渡す限りの本棚。<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>そのすべてにびっしりと本が詰まっている。<CLT>
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Look at all this stuff. It's hard to imagine what they\n"
"*don't* have in here.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>俺たちの他に人影はないみたいだけど…<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>さてどうしようか？<CLT>
msgctxt "0003"
msgid "There's a bunch of stuff laying around..."
msgstr ""

#. 暇つぶしによさそうだな
msgctxt "0004"
msgid "Yeah, totally."
msgstr ""

#. ふん…これだけの叡智を前に"暇つぶし"とは
#. 貴様もなかなか言うな。
msgctxt "0005"
msgid "But it's all junk. Who gives a shit about any of this?"
msgstr ""

#. それとも、貴様も感じているのか？
msgctxt "0006"
msgid "You wanna give the toy machine a shot?"
msgstr ""

#. この無数の書物の中に、まだ見ぬ真の魔術書が
#. 埋もれているという事を…
msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"Damn, they got one of those here? I had all kinds of\n"
"those toys when I was a kid!"
msgstr ""

#. ククク…どちらが先にその書を見つけられるか
#. 競ってみるのも面白いかもしれんな。
msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"I'd stand there staring at it, and my brother would\n"
"just walk up, bash it, and they'd all spill out!"
msgstr ""

#. 勉強が捗りそうだな
msgctxt "0009"
msgid "Ahh, good times."
msgstr ""

#. 貴様の言う"勉強"が何を指すかは知らんが
#. 確かにここは知識を得るための場だ。
msgctxt "0010"
msgid "Alright! Let's see who can find the rarest junk first!"
msgstr ""

#. この島では魔獣の養育場に続く
#. 重要施設といえるだろ。
msgctxt "0011"
msgid "Is that clock an antique?"
msgstr ""

#. 無数の叡智が納められた書架と静謐な空気…
#. 悪くない場所だ。
msgctxt "0012"
msgid "Looks like it prolly smells all moldy to me."
msgstr ""

#. 問題があるとすれば、ここは静かすぎて
#. 我が魔獣の存在を隠しきれぬという事くらいか…
msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"And it'd probably break the second you touched it.\n"
"Do people really collect shit like that?"
msgstr ""

#. 特にする事はないな…
msgctxt "0014"
msgid "What the hell's so great about it?"
msgstr ""

#. な、なんだと…？
msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. この場所の価値が分からんとは…
#. 所詮はただの人間か…
msgctxt "0016"
msgid "That vase looks pretty expensive..."
msgstr ""

#. ならば貴様とはもう話すことはない。
#. 勝手にどこへでも行くがいい。
msgctxt "0017"
msgid "Ugh, I can't hardly even move around in here."
msgstr ""

#. 専門書でも読むか…
msgctxt "0018"
msgid "Hey, watch out! You almost smacked it with your arm!"
msgstr ""

#. …面白い。
#. この俺様と目指す場所が同じとはな。
msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"Jeez... What if you knocked it over and it smashed\n"
"everywhere?"
msgstr ""

#. いいだろう、
#. 貴様には特別にこの俺様の愛読書を教えてやる。
msgctxt "0020"
msgid "Are you gonna buy something?"
msgstr ""

#. 読んだところで、貴様には到底
#. 理解出来ないだろうがな！
msgctxt "0021"
msgid "Oh, good idea. Maybe I'll get somethin' to eat."
msgstr ""

#. さぁ、まずは世界の魔獣図鑑から始めるぞ！
#. 付いてくるがいい！
msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"The food in the dining hall's okay, but sometimes ya\n"
"just want a pile of junk food, ya know?"
msgstr ""

#. 写真集でも見るか…
msgctxt "0023"
msgid "Let's see..."
msgstr ""

#. ふん…貴様にしては悪くない選択だ。
msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"Shit, they got everything here! Okay, what should I\n"
"get...?"
msgstr ""

#. こういう所には一般人には手に入れにくい
#. 貴重な物も置いてあるからな。
msgctxt "0025"
msgid "What's that ceramic looking thing?"
msgstr ""

#. 心ゆくまで世界の魔獣達の大図版を
#. 堪能するがいい！
msgctxt "0026"
msgid "How the hell should I know?"
msgstr ""

#. なんならこの俺様が直々に選んでやるぞ！
msgctxt "0027"
msgid "I mean seriously..."
msgstr ""

#. 小説でも読むか…
msgctxt "0028"
msgid "Did you really think I'd have any clue?"
msgstr ""

#. ふん…くだらんな。
msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 貴様は虚構の中から一片の真実を
#. 探し当てられると過信しているかもしれんが…
msgctxt "0030"
msgid "Are you gonna take a CD?"
msgstr ""

#. 俺様に言わせればそんなものは時間の無駄だ。
msgctxt "0031"
msgid "Maybe later, if I feel like it."
msgstr ""

#. 同じ時間を費やすのならば
#. もっと己が糧となるものを選ぶ事だな。
msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"I mean, don't get me wrong. It's not like I hate\n"
"music."
msgstr ""

#. この場所は危険だ…
msgctxt "0033"
msgid ""
"But I haven't really listened to much of it since\n"
"we've been in here."
msgstr ""

#. フッ…貴様も感じるか。
#. ここはすでに"奴"の結界の中だ。
msgctxt "0034"
msgid "Nothing here is really what I'm into, ya know?"
msgstr ""

#. 俺様たちを上手く誘い込んだつもりだろうが
#. この程度の術式を破るのは造作もない…
msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"Hey, so what kinda music are you into, Makoto? You\n"
"don't gotta go into detail, but ya know..."
msgstr ""

#. それよりも今は、
#. "奴"の目的を探ることに専念すべきだろう。
msgctxt "0036"
msgid "Have you ever played an accordion?"
msgstr ""

#. 世界の再構築を回避する為にもな…ククク…
msgctxt "0037"
msgid "An accordion?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>奴って誰なんだ…<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>とはきかない方がいいんだろうな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0038"
msgid "Shit no! Jesus, do you ever think before you talk?"
msgstr ""

#. 宝探しでもするか
msgctxt "0039"
msgid "There's tons of ceramics here..."
msgstr ""

#. …やめておけ。
msgctxt "0040"
msgid "Yeah, what's all this doin' in a school store?"
msgstr ""

#. 貴様のような素人が
#. 下手に首を突っ込めば…死ぬぞ。
msgctxt "0041"
msgid "Oh, maybe some kid here made all that stuff."
msgstr ""

#. それほどに図書館の"闇"とは昏きもの…
#. よく覚えておけ。
msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"There's gotta be some kinda \"Ultimate Ceramics Artist\"\n"
"or some shit out there, right?"
msgstr ""

#. 間違っても"開かずの書架"など見つけるなよ…
#. …いいな！？
msgctxt "0043"
msgid "But ya know...where's all the other students, anyway?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>それは、探せってことなのか…？<CLT>
msgctxt "0044"
msgid "This whole school is totally fuckin' weird..."
msgstr ""

#. 隠し扉でも探すか
msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
